Simple systemd unit file for ComicStreamer
1. Modify the file, changing the user, group, and path values to match your system's values
2. Run the following commands. This assumes your current working directory is the dir this README file is located in.
sudo cp comicstreamer.service /etc/systemd/service/
sudo systemctl enable comicstreamer.service
sudo systemctl start comicstreamer.service

Now ComicStreamer will automatically start when your server restarts.
